{"tid":1220222,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"千萬唔好鬆懈！六四前夕國內外輿論都係人民佔上風！","createTime":"2019-06-14T03:17:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T16:43:18.000Z","uid":8244,"like":427,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"988f3d3c4f221f1d66bf27e8cfd76dc4b64053b9","tid":1220222,"uid":8244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:17:27.000Z","msg":"六四前一個月嘅氣氛同而家好似<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1218506\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1218506</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n依家不論係<br />\n<br />\n媒體轉向 （明報今日社評）<br />\n<br />\n政府官員割蓆（陳建宗 湯渣）<br />\n<br />\n政府相關人士言論轉向 （陳智思）<br />\n<br />\n外國媒體大肆報導支持<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">上述類次既事六四前係全部有發生過！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我地一來要更認真去看待呢場仗</span><br />\n<br />\n我地好似不斷獲得小勝，但其實輸一次就已經輸哂<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">二來要避免得到 六四時既結局</span><br />\n<br />\n呢方面大家有無咩想法，對外宣傳當中強調我地可能會得到六四學生既下場，但我地別無他法，令外界（香港市民同外國政府）對中共/警察血腥鎮壓有警剔？"},{"pid":"34c0ba2710c6456a45de169662652dbde4771ccf","tid":1220222,"uid":8244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:18:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"592701c7683123dda7285c85e6a6b626a6a74739","tid":1220222,"uid":8244,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:20:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d6f3ae800ec85a654f9f6c3a5d1e9e8609f44cac","tid":1220222,"uid":18739,"like":76,"dislike":0,"score":76,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:30:31.000Z","msg":"六四同佔中的教訓&hellip;長期佔領就會被消磨意志，大家都以為好安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家要保存實力，化整為零呀！"},{"pid":"a3d2fcfbb00725abdd2a16c1976589204f3d4240","tid":1220222,"uid":141597,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:33:05.000Z","msg":"主流媒體啲風一定唔係為咗割蓆，咁吹法一定係有目的。而共媒無論係咩目的都唔慌係好，唔好俾連登啲恥笑割蓆post上晒熱門！<br />\n<br />\n花生食少少振奮一下就夠，唔好打晒飛機！！！！<br />\n<br />\n保持警覺，唔好因爲少少轉風向就鬆繲！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1220007\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1220007</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"306d75a6522ba711241154ae8f7382c42a5715aa","tid":1220222,"uid":2419,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:33:58.000Z","msg":"拒絕階段性勝利"},{"pid":"cf2a067bdc377946cc8bcfab961899552b3caa63","tid":1220222,"uid":258736,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:37:24.000Z","msg":"冇錯!國際上輿論要有,但人民自身的反抗都好重要,當年六四發生喺北京,有太多限制。但今日發生喺香港,中共唔會妄然出兵,所以我一定要長期行動,逼到政府撤回法案"},{"pid":"1d4d938ace821c8e0dbd1a53b983f394670d773a","tid":1220222,"uid":138609,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:43:49.000Z","msg":"政府有時間上既死線<br />\n拖越耐政府就越急<br />\n一急就會自亂陣腳<br />\n今次同雨傘最大既分別<br />\n就係政府無時間拖"},{"pid":"0ca459617c210823c41dd495b8b889d7c548ab41","tid":1220222,"uid":24133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:46:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f842ac29955c7ed2369e614ce2ba20a738ea5b46","tid":1220222,"uid":8244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:08:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"edf4ba20b8d84a3b57267e602c8dcbb5b8ca14b9","tid":1220222,"uid":8244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:09:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b2194df020b212d3d9a92d3783fad2b4940f17cc","tid":1220222,"uid":8244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:11:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2fbf492c19f9eb82f4ca2ee0d8000a5e2fc282a6","tid":1220222,"uid":255373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:14:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9152cee3e2337822712612844faed58d7df4e727","tid":1220222,"uid":36089,"like":0,"dislike